tens of thousands of yuan, I wouldn't

101
00:06:33,690 --> 00:06:34,530
be haunted by such unease.

102
00:06:35,710 --> 00:06:36,750
If you hadn't opened the doors

103
00:06:36,770 --> 00:06:37,780
to easy money for me,

104
00:06:38,130 --> 00:06:40,010
I wouldn't be waiting around for victims.

105
00:06:41,020 --> 00:06:42,610
If you hadn't inspired this idea of scamming others,

106
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:44,140
I wouldn't be loitering here all day.

107
00:06:44,230 --> 00:06:44,880
Well,

108
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,230
who else can I blame for this?

109
00:06:49,180 --> 00:06:51,540
I guess it's true.

110
00:06:51,540 --> 00:06:52,770
There's a master in every trade.

111
00:06:53,540 --> 00:06:55,580
It's a miracle that a top-tier jerk

112
00:06:55,580 --> 00:06:56,940
like Wang Zhishui can be born.

113
00:06:58,960 --> 00:07:01,060
But every douchebag

114
00:07:01,080 --> 00:07:02,560
has a heart-wrenching past.

115
00:07:02,930 --> 00:07:04,450
