120
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:16,420
Let go.

121
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:26,790
What's your name?

122
00:07:28,150 --> 00:07:28,870
Wang Zhishui.

123
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:29,720
Bullshit!

124
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:31,420
I tried to look you up.

125
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:33,020
Wang Zhishui doesn't exist.

126
00:07:33,740 --> 00:07:34,460
I don't have a registered household.

127
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:35,580
Where are you from?

128
00:07:36,490 --> 00:07:37,130
Shandong.

129
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,310
Did you come up to the north?

130
00:07:45,700 --> 00:07:46,930
My elder sister drowned in a flood.

131
00:07:47,850 --> 00:07:49,090
That's why my name is Wang Zhishui.

132
00:07:50,310 --> 00:07:51,790
My parents divorced when I was very young.

133
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,330
My mom remarried.

134
00:07:54,100 --> 00:07:55,740
My dad sold all his properties and fled.

135
00:07:56,980 --> 00:07:58,170
I was left behind with my grandma.

136
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:00,780
I dropped out of school in junior high

137
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,730
and started working as a waiter at thirteen years old.

138
00:08:03,350 --> 00:08:04,750
I only earned ¥240 a month.

139
00:08:06,030 --> 00:08:07,310
After that, my grandma passed away.

140
00:08:08,350 --> 00:08:10,160
My uncle had grudges against my dad,

141
00:08:10,660 --> 00:08:12,070
so no one wanted to take me in.

142
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:14,000
That's why I came to Beijing.

143
00:08:14,930 --> 00:08:16,240
I've been here for eight years,

144
00:08:16,460 --> 00:08:17,330
without a proper place to stay.

145
00:08:17,810 --> 00:08:18,660
I sleep at the train station

146
00:08:18,970 --> 00:08:20,100
or the lobby of hospitals.

147
00:08:20,730 --> 00:08:22,570
How can I get hired without a degree?

148
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:24,610
I can only work as a laborer or a vendor.

149
00:08:25,260 --> 00:08:26,640
Sometimes, I go to the zoo to resell clothes.

150
00:08:27,260 --> 00:08:27,980
The money I earn

151
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,300
isn't even worth stealing.

152
00:08:31,900 --> 00:08:32,940
When I met you,

153
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,440
I had less than ¥20 with me.

154
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,730
I wanted to sneak some drinks at the bar,

155
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:38,480
but I was kicked out.

156
00:08:39,130 --> 00:08:40,750
In the end, you carried me home.

157
00:08:41,299 --> 00:08:43,120
You gave me ¥1,000 so easily.

158
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:44,960
I was tempted.

159
00:08:45,740 --> 00:08:46,330
I'm telling the truth.

160
00:08:46,860 --> 00:08:47,900
If you hadn't bullied me,

161
00:08:47,900 --> 00:08:49,140
I wouldn't have stolen your things.

162
00:08:49,530 --> 00:08:51,000
I took that damn money home

163
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:52,130
