167
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:00,620
Brother.

168
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:01,840
Brother.

169
00:09:02,820 --> 00:09:03,840
I'm begging you.

170
00:09:04,300 --> 00:09:05,850
Take me to the police station.

171
