186
00:10:09,340 --> 00:10:10,740
I found Wang Zhishui.

187
00:10:11,690 --> 00:10:12,460
Did you find him?

188
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:14,620
Where did you find him?

189
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:15,530
Where is he now?

190
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:17,220
Listen to me.

191
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:32,220
Were you cheated?

192
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:33,260
That's impossible.

193
00:10:33,920 --> 00:10:34,880
He wouldn't dare lie to me.

194
00:10:37,330 --> 00:10:37,810
That's true.

195
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:39,890
Con men hardly con the same person twice.

196
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:43,780
What time is it?

197
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:55,420
Didn't you buy a new watch?

198
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:56,560
Why aren't you wearing it?

199
00:10:58,920 --> 00:10:59,340
Brother.

200
00:11:00,280 --> 00:11:01,320
I'm begging you.

201
00:11:01,860 --> 00:11:03,300
Take me to the police station.

202
00:11:24,140 --> 00:11:24,940
Wang Zhishui.

203
00:11:25,600 --> 00:11:26,520
I'll drown you in my urine

204
