248
00:14:10,270 --> 00:14:12,230
I haven't worn thermal pants in ages.

249
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:14,540
Why so smug?

250
00:14:15,570 --> 00:14:16,740
I'm not being smug.

251
00:14:17,210 --> 00:14:18,550
This is my attitude.

252
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:21,600
I will not be defeated by Mother Nature.

253
00:14:30,630 --> 00:14:31,220
Manager,

254
00:14:31,300 --> 00:14:31,660
come over here.

255
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:32,740
Coming.

256
00:14:35,370 --> 00:14:36,390
Leave a little later today.

257
00:14:37,020 --> 00:14:38,410
