265
00:14:50,470 --> 00:14:51,670
from my private funds.

266
00:14:52,620 --> 00:14:53,140
Yes, okay.

267
00:14:53,490 --> 00:14:54,230
All right, get going.

268
00:15:23,860 --> 00:15:24,570
It's warm.

269
00:15:25,050 --> 00:15:26,290
The heater is turned on really early.

270
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:33,300
Folks,

271
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:34,650
