272
00:15:34,780 --> 00:15:36,580
We're conducting underwater combat training today.

273
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:37,760
Xia Yao, hurry.

274
00:15:37,990 --> 00:15:38,390
Yes.

275
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,430
Everyone is assembled.

276
00:16:35,770 --> 00:16:36,220
At ease.

277
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:41,540
Underwater combat training

278
00:16:42,180 --> 00:16:43,790
is a comprehensive practical skill.

279
00:16:46,090 --> 00:16:47,270
Due to the buoyancy,

280
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:49,060
resistance, pressure,

281
00:16:49,590 --> 00:16:50,910
and thermal conductivity of water,

282
00:16:51,460 --> 00:16:52,480
underwater combat requires

283
00:16:52,660 --> 00:16:54,780
even more well-rounded physical fitness.

284
00:16:56,020 --> 00:16:56,610
Today,

285
00:16:56,780 --> 00:16:57,670
we'll be conducting basic

286
00:16:57,850 --> 00:16:59,180
underwater combat training.

287
00:17:00,090 --> 00:17:00,550
Mr. Yuan

288
00:17:00,990 --> 00:17:02,410
